                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260914-122-off719 t18260914-122-cd720"></join>, 1 handkerchief, value 6d.; 1 coat, value 10s.; 1 pair of breeches, value 5s., and 1 waistcoat, value 1s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18260914-122-victim841" type="victimName">
                        Michael 
